Note: ============================================================================

Note: BUILD_OPT_BASIC = O1. This is the ratified Q3 default for the
Note: legacy single-file driver path (compiler_driver.runa) which does
Note: not instantiate a BuildContext. Matches optimize_function's
Note: interpretation of opt_level=1 = "O1 basic optimizations".
Constant BUILD_OPT_NONE_LOCAL as Integer is 0
Constant BUILD_OPT_BASIC as Integer is 1
Constant BUILD_OPT_STANDARD as Integer is 2
Constant BUILD_OPT_AGGRESSIVE_LOCAL as Integer is 3

